(1456, 494, 'yes', 'greenbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that the solutions discussed and finalised to overcome the challenges are being implemented. It is very important to implement the solutions in order to overcome the challenges as then only will you be able to overcome all the challenges and obstacles.</span></span></p>\r\n', '20', 'Implementation of Solutions'),
(1457, 494, 'no', 'redbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that the solutions discussed and finalised to overcome the challenges are not being implemented. If the solutions arrived at are not implemented, it will not serve any purpose. It is essential to implement the solutions to overcome the challenges.</span></span></p>\r\n', '10', 'Implementation of Solutions'),
(1458, 495, 'yes', 'greenbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that you have a monitoring mechanism to monitor how effectively solutions to overcome challenges are being implemented. It is very important to have a real time monitoring mechanism to track implementation of the solutions.</span></span></p>\r\n', '20', 'Monitoring Mechanism'),
(1459, 495, 'no', 'redbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that you do not have a monitoring mechanism to monitor how effectively solutions to overcome challenges are being implemented. If there is no monitoring mechanism to track implementation of solutions, it would be difficult to find out the effectiveness of these solutions.</span></span></p>\r\n', '0', 'Monitoring Mechanism'),
(1460, 496, 'More business with existing customers\r\n', 'greenbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that one of the current opportunities for growth is &ldquo;more business with existing customers&rdquo;. If your product quality is good and your pricing is right, then winning more business from existing customers is usually the easiest place to harvest opportunities.</span></span></p>\r\n', '10', ''),
(1461, 496, 'New customers\r\n', 'greenbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that one of the current opportunities for growth is through acquiring new customers. Unless your product set is unique or priced extremely competitively, it may be relatively difficult to convert opportunities into new business. Nevertheless, you cannot afford to simply rely on your existing customer base, particularly if there&nbsp;are competitors that can provide similar products at similar value and thereby steal your share of the customer&rsquo;s purse.</span></span></p>\r\n', '10', ''),
(1462, 496, 'New Markets\r\n', 'greenbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that one of the current opportunities for growth is by entering new markets. Entering new markets can be risky unless &nbsp;you have a sustainable competitive advantage that cannot be easily matched in your newly chosen markets. Watch out for substitutes or predatory pricing from competitors.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n', '10', ''),
(1463, 496, 'New Products\r\n', 'greenbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that one of the current opportunities for growth is by selling new products. Selling new products to existing customers can be relatively easy, particularly if there is market demand for the products. Selling new products into new markets attracts a great deal of risk.</span></span></p>\r\n', '10', ''),
(1464, 496, 'None\r\n', 'redbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that there are no opportunities for growth. If you have no opportunities at all this is extremely dangerous for your business unless your business is already at full capacity. You cannot afford to stand still as other competitors will always be looking to win some of your existing business from your customers. If you are not&nbsp;moving forward by selling to new customers, selling in new markets or selling new products then your business could easily decline.</span></span></p>\r\n', '0', ''),
(1465, 497, 'yes', 'greenbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">It is heartening to know that the opportunities are being pursued aggressively. The same should be continued and the result of persuasion should be monitored to &nbsp;evaluate that you are moving in the right direction or if any change is required</span></span></p>\r\n', '15', ''),
(1466, 497, 'no', 'redbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Efforts should be made to aggressively pursue the opportunities else the competitors might gain advantage by encashing on these opportunities.</span></span></p>\r\n', '0', ''),
(1467, 498, 'yes', 'greenbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that you have an active sales pipeline in your business. You should ensure that you are getting the following benefits out of it:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Shows the status and accounts of sales representatives</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Shows the value and quantity of success in each stage of business dealings</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Allows the company to forecast</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">The possible revenue</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Gives you a clear report on the critical financial metrics in business</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Allows you to score your leads</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Offers better opportunities to assign the right leads to the right salespeople in the company</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Helps increase the productivity of your sales team</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Translates to higher revenue growth for the company.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sales pipelines make it easier for you to schedule follow-ups</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '25', 'Sales Pipeline'),
(1468, 498, 'no', 'redbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">You mentioned that you do not have an active sales pipeline in your business. You need to work on creating an efficient sales pipeline as it will give the following benefits:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Shows the status and accounts of sales representatives</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Shows the value and quantity of success in each stage of business dealings</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Allows the company to forecast the possible revenue</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Gives you a clear report on the critical financial metrics in business</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Allows you to score your leads</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Offers better opportunities to assign the right leads to the right salespeople in the company</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Helps increase the productivity of your sales team</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Translates to higher revenue growth for the company.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sales pipelines make it easier for you to schedule follow-ups</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '0', 'Sales Pipeline'),
(1469, 499, 'yes', 'greenbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Since you are already using CRM, you should see whether you are getting the following benefits from your CRM:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Better customer service</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Increased sales</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Improved customer retention</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Detailed analytics</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Higher productivity and efficiency</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Centralized database of information</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Managed communications with prospective leads</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Improved customer segmentation</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Automated sales reports</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">More accurate sales forecasting</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Streamlined internal communications</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">In case you are not getting these benefits you need to review your CRM and make necessary modifications/upgradations if required.</span></span></p>\r\n', '20', 'CRM'),
