(1627, 492, 'Occasionally', 'redbullet.png', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Since you mentioned that the company addresses the challenges occasionally, the company should address all the key challenges very promptly. This will help to overcome them in a timely manner.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n', '2', 'Frequency of Addressing Challenges'),
